	'637' => {
		message => q|<p><strong>Keresztn&eacute;v</strong><br />   A felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; keresztneve. </p>  <p><strong>K&ouml;z&eacute;pső n&eacute;v</strong><br /> A felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; k&ouml;z&eacute;pső neve. </p>  <p><strong>Vezet&eacute;kn&eacute;v</strong><br /> A felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; vezet&eacute;k (csal&aacute;d) neve. </p>  <p><strong>Email C&iacute;m</strong><br /> Felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; e-mail c&iacute;me. Csak akkor kell megadni, ha a felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; olyan funkci&oacute;t l&aacute;t el, amelynek ell&aacute;t&aacute;s&aacute;hoz sz&uuml;ks&eacute;ges az e-mail c&iacute;m. </p>  <p><strong>ICQ UIN</strong><br /> The <a href="http://www.icq.com/">ICQ</a> UIN is the &quot;User ID Number&quot; on the ICQ network. ICQ is a very popular instant messaging platform. </p>  <p><strong>AIM Id</strong><br /> The account id for the <a href="http://www.aim.com/">AOL Instant Messenger</a> system. </p>  <p><strong>MSN Messenger Id</strong><br /> The account id for the <a href="http://messenger.msn.com/">Microsoft Network Instant Messenger</a> system. </p>  <p><strong>Yahoo! Messenger Id</strong><br /> The account id for the <a href="http://messenger.yahoo.com/">Yahoo! Instant Messenger</a> system. </p>  <p><strong>Mobiltelefon</strong><br />  A felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; mobil telefonsz&aacute;ma.</p>  <p><strong>Pager</strong><br /> This user&#39;s pager telephone number. </p>  <p><strong>Email To Pager Gateway</strong><br /> This user&#39;s text pager email address. </p>  <p><strong>Otthoni C&iacute;m</strong><br /> A felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; otthoni levelez&eacute;si c&iacute;me. </p>  <p><strong>Munkahelyi C&iacute;m</strong><br /> A felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute;  munkahelyi levelez&eacute;si c&iacute;me. </p>  <p><strong>Nem</strong><br /> A felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; neme. </p>  <p><strong>Sz&uuml;let&eacute;si idő</strong><br /> A felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; sz&uuml;let&eacute;si ideje. </p>  <p><strong>Nyelv</strong><br />  A rendszer&uuml;zenetek megjelen&iacute;t&eacute;s&eacute;nek nyelve. </p>  <p><strong>Időelt&eacute;r&eacute;s</strong><br /> A server idej&eacute;től val&oacute; elt&eacute;r&eacute;s. Az időz&oacute;n&aacute;khoz val&oacute; alkalmazkod&aacute;shoz haszn&aacute;lj&aacute;k.</p>  <p><strong>A H&eacute;t Első Napja</strong><br /> A felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; helyi napt&aacute;r&aacute;nak első napja. P&eacute;ld&aacute;ul az USA-ban a h&eacute;t első napja a vas&aacute;rnap, m&iacute;g Eur&oacute;p&aacute;ban a legt&ouml;bb orsz&aacute;gban h&eacute;tfő.</p>  <p><strong>D&aacute;tum Form&aacute;tum</strong><br /> Milyen form&aacute;tumban jelenjenek meg a d&aacute;tumok? </p>  <p><strong>Idő Form&aacute;tum</strong><br /> Milyen form&aacute;tumban jelenjenek meg az időpontok?</p>  <p><strong>Discussion Layout</strong><br /> Should discussions be laid out flat or threaded? Flat puts all replies on one page in the order they were created. Threaded shows the hierarchical list of replies as they were created. </p>  <p><strong>Inbox Notifications</strong><br /> How should this user be notified when they get a new WebGUI message? </p>|,
		lastUpdated => 1178706314
	},

